OL,3,CWales' disability employment gap is
OL,4,Cthe worst in Britain
OL,6,FThe Engage to Change Ambassador for
OL,7,FLearning Disability, Gerraint Jones-
OL,8,FGriffiths believes employers need to
OL,9,Frealise the potential that people with
OL,10,Flearning disabilities can bring to the
OL,11,Fworkforce.
OL,13,FHe told the Committee: "I've always
OL,14,Fsaid, 'With the right support,
OL,15,Fanything is achievable.' I've always
OL,16,Fhad the motto that is 'A is not for
OL,17,Fautism, A is for achievement', and if
OL,18,Fpublic sector bodies, Welsh
OL,19,FGovernment, and all employers could
OL,20,Fsee this, there would be a massively
OL,21,Fbetter society for all to enjoy."
