OL,3,CWales' disability employment gap is
OL,4,Cthe worst in Britain
OL,6,FThe report found that false
OL,7,Fassumptions and negative attitudes
OL,8,Ftowards disabled people still persist,
OL,9,Fand over a quarter (26%) of disabled
OL,10,Fpeople say employers had failed to
OL,11,Fmake reasonable adjustments for them.
OL,13,FThe chair of the Equality and Social
OL,14,FJustice Committee, Jenny Rathbone MS
OL,15,Fsaid too many people with impairments
OL,16,Fcontinue to face barriers to work.
