OL,3,CWales' disability employment gap is
OL,4,Cthe worst in Britain
OL,6,FShe said: "We recognise that some
OL,7,Fimpairments mean that not everyone can
OL,8,Fwork, but we need action by teachers,
OL,9,Femployers and government to address
OL,10,Fthe underlying causes of the
OL,11,Fdisability employment gap.
OL,13,F"If we can tackle the disability
OL,14,Femployment gap, we'll see new talent
OL,15,Fin the workforce, an end to unrealised
OL,16,Fpotential, and improved prospects for
OL,17,Fthe whole of Wales."
