OL,3,CWales' disability employment gap is
OL,4,Cthe worst in Britain
OL,6,FIn a statement the Welsh Government
OL,7,Fsaid: "We provide support through our
OL,8,FBusiness Wales service and Disabled
OL,9,FPeople's Employment Champions network,
OL,10,Fhelping employers create more
OL,11,Finclusive workplaces.
OL,13,F"Our Disabled People's Rights Plan,
OL,14,Fwhich will be consulted on in Spring
OL,15,F2025, aims to further eliminate
OL,16,Fbarriers and enhance participation for
OL,17,Fall disabled people in Wales.
OL,19,F"We will consider the Committee's
OL,20,Ffindings and recommendations before
OL,21,Fresponding formally."
